UID:p6hpNUO28aDenV42rdTSd
SUMMARY:Alvin Ailey American Dance Theater
DTSTAMP:20260318T064956Z
DTSTART:20260321T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Paramount Theatre is located in downtown Seattle at 911 Pin
	e Street\, Seattle\, WA 98101. There is an 9 ticket limit for this event. 
	Accounts found in violation of the posted ticket limit may be cancelled wi
	thout notice. No late seating. All sales are final. No refunds or exchange
	s. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the
	 right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person mu
	st have a ticket regardless of age. There is no elevator. Stairs only to t
	he balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive early. No 
	weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety There is no elevator. Stairs onl
	y to the balcony level. When purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please fe
	el free to contact us by email or phone if any assistance is needed with a
	ccommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us by email at accessib
	ility@stgpresents.org or call us at 206-682-1414 ext. 5. Each accessible s
	eat houses an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairm
	ents and their companions. The freestanding chair can be removed to accomm
	odate a wheelchair.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/alvin-ailey-american-d
	ance-theater-seattle-washington-03-20-2026/event/0F0062C9E65A36FF\n\nFrom 
	STG - Paramount Theatre
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/alvin-ailey-american-dance-theater-seattle
